Flip flow screens have been taking more and more market portions in the last decade and users are typically very happy with the performance offered by this technology. However, some aspects of these machines are sometimes disappointing who works with them. As in every other industrial field defects can be solved or anyway reduced. In this view, Eurogomma has worked to use the qualities of our patented GET flexy system in order to improve some characteristics of the flip flow screeners. We have recently applied GET flexy to a Liwell*  LF 2.0 – 7.56/36 ED – big.